  80  function checkModule($moduleName) 
  81  {
  82      global $module, $instrument_id_base, $showScore;
  83      $tabQualifies = FALSE;
  84      $requirements = $module[$moduleName];    // look up the requirements for this report module

  85      // check if the instrument_id is valid

  86      if (strpos($requirements, $instrument_id_base) OR strpos($requirements, "ALL")) 
  87      { $tabQualifies = TRUE; }
  88      else { return FALSE; }
  89      if (strpos($requirements, "SCORE")) {
  90          if ($showScore == "yes") { $tabQualifies = TRUE; }
  91          else { return FALSE; }
  92      }
  93      return $tabQualifies;
  94  }
